      "fn_code": "static struct x86_process_info *\nx86_find_process_pid (pid_t pid)\n{\n  struct x86_process_info *proc;\n\n  for (proc = x86_process_list; proc; proc = proc->next)\n    if (proc->pid == pid)\n      return proc;\n\n  return NULL;\n}",
